Own shares in VentureCrowd

VentureCrowd is Australia’s leading multi-asset class investment platform for alternative assets.

Open to retail and wholesale investors, VentureCrowd’s open technology platform democratises alternative asset investing and facilitates access to purpose driven, sustainable investment opportunities in the following investment categories:

  • Venture capital including equity and debt securities
  • Property development including equity & preference equity
  • Alternative credit including mezzanine debt, first mortgage loans
  • Funds including diversified property funds

About the Offer

The business is profitable and is on track to deliver over $6.01M in revenue in FY21. Having built strong core infrastructure and generated profitable revenue growth, the business is now entering its most ambitious growth phase yet and is raising a small round to fast-track that growth.

  • Ordinary shares at a $21m Pre-money Valuation.
  • $25,000 Minimum Investment
  • 1.65% p.a. Mananagement Fee
  • 1.1% once off Contribution Fee
  • Open for Wholesale Investors
